1. Create directory
mkdir /kanapi_0.7
cd /kanapi_0.7

2. Download rootfs
https://sourceforge.net/projects/kanapi/files/packages/v0.7/rootfs/i686-rootfs.tar.xz/download

3. Uncompress rootfs
tar -xJf i686-root.tar.xz

4. Download pkg script and copy it to your $PATH
https://sourceforge.net/projects/kanapi/files/packages/v0.7/pkg/download

5. Download all packages
cd /kanapi_0.7/i686/packages
pkg pull_all

6. Uncompress all packages
for i in *.xz; do tar -xJf $i ; done

7. Run selected programs from /kanapi_0.7/i686/bin or from package directory
   /kanapi_0.7/i686/packages/"package name"/bin

If anything doesn't work, let me know, so I can fix it ;)

Enjoy!

